{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey through the world as a young lynx cub in the standalone, single player adventure Paws \u2013 A Shelter 2 Game. Traverse a vast and harrowing landscape together with your companion. Together you will follow tracks, fend off threats and overcome obstacles as you try to make your way home.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About <strong>Paws</strong>:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;Dark and grime, twist through the vines,</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Slip through perils with finesse and toil.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Be two for strength, be two of mind,</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Find the way home to familiar soil.&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Paws \u2013 A Shelter 2 Game combines all the unique elements from the beloved Shelter game series to present a lovingly crafted story about loss, friendship and a search for lost love. Venture out in the world and make your way home. An amazing journey awaits you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Main features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A gripping, narrative experience in a fantasy setting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For the first time ever in the Shelter world, you play as a young lynx cub accompanied by a companion to help complete puzzles and overcome obstacles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New gameplay features include the ability to follow tracks using your sense ability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New original music from Retro Family.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A whole new corner of the world of Shelter to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"An introduction","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/434000/0e313584